            <p>
                Finding the right size for your child is essential for their comfort and style. Use our size guide to ensure the perfect fit for clothing and shoes.
            </p>

            <h3><strong>Clothing Size Guide</strong></h3>
            <p>
                <strong>Tops & Bottoms:</strong> Measure your child's chest, waist, and hips to find the best size. Refer to our size chart for accurate measurements corresponding to age or specific measurements.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Dresses & Jumpsuits:</strong> Consider chest, waist, and length measurements to select the appropriate size. Follow our size guide for accurate fitting.
            </p>

            <h3><strong>Shoe Size Guide</strong></h3>
            <p>
                <strong>Foot Length:</strong> Measure your child's foot from heel to toe. Use our shoe size chart to match the length to the correct shoe size.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Width:</strong> Consider the foot width for a comfortable fit. Our size chart includes width measurements for each size.
            </p>

            <h3><strong>Additional Tips</strong></h3>
            <p>
                - If unsure about sizes, opt for a size up rather than a size down to allow room for growth.
            </p>
            <p>
                - Check product descriptions for specific size recommendations and guidelines.
            </p>
            <p>
                - Feel free to contact our customer support team for personalized size advice and assistance.
